<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Primrose" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Primrose,</orth> the flower Primula: <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.122" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 122</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.63" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 63</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.5.83" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 5, 83</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.221" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 221</bibl>. Adjectively: <cit><quote>this p. bank,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 151" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 151</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>p. beds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 1.1.215" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. I, 1, 215</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>go the p. way to the everlasting bonfire,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 2.3.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 3, 21</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the p. path of dalliance,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 1.3.50" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 3, 50</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>